T2  - Management Science
JF  - Management Science
JO  - Management Science
SP  - 931
EP  - 938
VL  - 33
IS  - 7
PB  - INFORMS
N2  - The overflow process from a G/M/N/K queueing system with a stationary counting arrival process, Markovian service times, N parallel homogeneous servers, and K waiting spaces, is asymptotically approximated by a two parameter method. Numerical results are presented and approximation outcomes are compared against those from a simulation study.
AB  - The overflow process from a G/M/N/K queueing system with a stationary counting arrival process, Markovian service times, N parallel homogeneous servers, and K waiting spaces, is asymptotically approximated by a two parameter method. Numerical results are presented and approximation outcomes are compared against those from a simulation study.
